name: Е
description: Technology and new formats are developing rapidly. And here we see art becoming digital as well. And it seems strange how it is possible to possess not a physical object, but only a digital certificate. Nft format for me, a new and not yet very clear thing. But it is interesting. I'm sure it will transform and change many times, but I'm sure that digital art will be with us for a long time. It's futuristic.
